> Objective_2: Display the text of the child component in the main component

Children.js

1 ) Define Children component
— React component it is a JavaScript function
2 ) Display Hi, I am Children component heading in the <h2> HTML tag
— Some functions may return result
3 ) Export Children component using named export
— Use reserved statement in JavaScript to do this (one word)

App.js

1 ) Import Children component from ./Children.js using named import
— Use reserved statement in JavaScript to do this (one word)
2 ) Display Children component in the App component
— Syntax to display React component is similar to HTML tags syntax